==== ENTRY 5 ====
HEADWORD: Allay
<hw>Al*lay"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To mix (metals); to mix with a
baser metal; to alloy; to deteriorate.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>
<rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

